\id 2JN - Muyuw NT [myw] -Papua New Guinea 1993 (web version -2014)
\h 2 Yon
\toc1 2 YON
\toc2 2 Yon
\toc3 2 Yon
\mt1 2 YON
\ip Yon nakalelel kwayuwein let towen waseg silawun sinap mounid.
\c 1
\s1 Nakabsilamaw
\p 
\v 1 Yey tamwey, gunalet niwekeimiy bukuvinis numwey yak simwey nitum. Peinan Yeisuw angamag yakamiy. Singay ikalin nuwem yakamiy, sigwey tasiyas babaw isimounids Yeisuw waseg.
\p 
\v 2 Ikalin nuwads peinan sinap mounid nises wasigeis ya̱kids; e, wasigeis ya̱kids bises bisigeg.
\p 
\v 3 Sivinag Tamads Yowbad binok nuwan wasigeis yakamiy, bisiwyoubumiy, mo beitaw nuwamiy. Natun-vak Yeisuw Kelis mounid bilabeimiy, siwa̱youb waseg.
\s1 Kuyyousis Kelis nakaleiwag
\p 
\v 4 Bo amwa̱saw peinan bo aban nitum asisinap kamnat, bwanabwein; iyyousis Tamads nakaleiwag, towen nisekeids.
\p 
\v 5 Numwey yak, tut towen akagma̱num waseg yak, kadiloka bukuvnas kaleiwag towen wanmugwana nises. Nag balel kweivaw kaleiwag, nag; misinaka kaleiwag kweiboug mamagina bitasiwa̱youbs sidsidayas wasigeis.
\p 
\v 6 Kukin bitasiwa̱youbs beibwein mo bitavna̱ses Towen nakaleiwag. Nakaleiwag towen, wanmugwana nukuliganes, mamagina siwa̱youb waseg.
\p 
\v 7 Tasiyas takatidavidavs babaw nisaps wadaban pwepway; asilivan kalbaleb; nag isimounids Mesay imlavag gamag towen Yeisuw. Tapiyaveins Kelis tasiyas.
\p 
\v 8 Kadiloka bukutoukums; awoum bukuyamkwaneimiy maysan miwotet. Kadiloka meiveka bukuyousis.
\p 
\v 9 Kukin kal bipiyev liva̱nen Kelis, mo bipiyev Yowbad. Tage kal yak bukuyyous liva̱nen Kelis waseg, Tamads Yowbad son Natun mo bukusesus simwey ya̱koum.
\p 
\v 10 Magat teitan beiw, tapiyavein livan towen, awoum kutam ambwabwal towen; awoum bukumulouls soum, awoum.
\p 
\v 11 Kukin bukumuloul soum mo bukuleb nawotet kalbaleb waseg.
\s1 Taneimiy-o
\p 
\v 12 Sinap babaw bakatimlakeimiy, adok awoum balel let towen waseg, peinan sivinag bawekeimiy bitakaypuls sigwey yakamiy, balivan wamitamiy; adok mo bitamwa̱saws avakaein.
\p 
\v 13 Bwadam nitun ikalin nuwes wasigeis yakamiy, bwadam towen Yeisuw angamag teitan. Taneimiy-o.
\p Yey Yon. 
